reviewText: Lousy. I did not expect this.
Love this movie, is hilarious and with the best Silvia Navarro y Jorge Salinas.
Watching their soap opera on TV and now this movie you realize their  range in acting. It's so well made you think they are your friends confining their personal story, very real.
The movie is with my favorites Mexican actors, Silvia Navarro and Jorge Salinas, extraordinary, I love both and the entire movie.

I enjoyed this movie. It had some funny parts. Both Silvia Navarro (huge fan of hers) and Jorge Salinas are great actors and they did a good job. I just wished that the movie was a bit longer and showed a little more of the woman's perspective on the subject.
